#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"Corporate photography is more than just taking pictures of your employees, "
"products, or events. It is a powerful way to communicate your brand "
"identity, values, and personality to your potential customers, partners, and"
